         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Meredith ¶ Octr 8th 1883 ¶ Dear Sir ¶  ¶ I forward with this seven fresh specimens to me. ¶  ¶ Our school botanical collection is daily being added to, the children taking great interest in it....</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">83.10.08a</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">From Sidney Johnson</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">RB MSS M12, Library, Royal Botanic Gardens Melbourne.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">MS found with a specimen of <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Melicytus denatatus</seg> (MEL 2230153). MS annotation by M: 'Answ 9/10/83. F.v.M.' Letter not found.</p>
               </note>Meredith<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Vic.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Octr 8th 1883</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Dear Sir</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I forward with this seven fresh specimens to me.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Our school botanical collection is daily being added to, the children taking great interest in it.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>In a recent issue of the "Age" a plant was described as "<name key="Avaena%20Languisorbae">Avaena Languisorbae</name>" I have the same plant but spelt "<name key="Acaena%20Sanguisorbae">Acaena Sanguisorbae</name>" Will you kindly say which is correct<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>See <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Age</seg> (Melbourne), 1 October 1883, p. 5: 'A number of animals were discovered dead in a field … the cause of death was a small plant with bright red flowers and a kind of burr. [Baron von Mueller reported that] the burr which caused the mischief … is Avaena languisorbae'. <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Acaena</seg>
                     <seg style="font-style: italic; "> sanguisorbae</seg> is correct.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>With many thanks for former kindness</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">I remain</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>yours Truly</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Sidney Johnson</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Acaena%20Sanguisorbae">Acaena Sanguisorbae</name>
            </p>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Avaena%20Languisorbae">Avaena Languisorbae</name>
            </p>
